      {
        "duration": 4.02,
        "end_time": 4.02,
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "text": "The birch can use lid on the smooth planks."
      },
      {
        "duration": 2.02,
        "end_time": 6.64,
        "start_time": 4.62,
        "text": "Glue the sheet to the dark blue background."
      },
      {
        "duration": 2.62,
        "end_time": 10.5,
        "start_time": 7.88,
        "text": "It is easy to tell the depth of a well."
      },
      {
        "duration": 3.12,
        "end_time": 14.04,
        "start_time": 10.92,
        "text": "These days, the chicken leg is a rare dish."
      },
      {
        "duration": 5.82,
        "end_time": 20.16,
        "start_time": 14.34,
        "text": "Rice is often served in round bowls. The juice of lemons makes fine punch."
      },
      {
        "duration": 9.86,
        "end_time": 30.3,
        "start_time": 20.44,
        "text": "The box was thrown beside the pork chuck. The hogs were fed chopped corn and garbage. hours of steady work faced us, a"
      },
      {
        "duration": 7.14,
        "end_time": 37.44,
        "start_time": 30.3,
        "text": "large size in stockings is hard to sell."
      }
    ]
  },
